                     <interp inst="t18120916-78-off444" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18120916-78-cd445" type="crimeDate">9th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18120916-78-off444 t18120916-78-cd445"></join>, a silk handkerchief, value 2 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18120916-78-victim638" type="victimName">
